Text.string: Coop is avenged! And Inquisitor Bloodflap sure as hell won't be runnin' anyone down anymore—not now that he's all exploded into a fine mist like that. Come on back and let me thank you, Vault Hunter.

I know our planet may not look like much, but Eden-6 is run by Jakobs, and Jakobs ain't like all them other corporations. It's a family. We do the work, and they keep us from gettin' killed. Jakobs has stood for three hundred years and we can't let the old tree fall now.
Things may look bad for us, but the swamp folk are strong and we ain't gonna take this invasion lyin' down. I'll always remember what you did for Coop, Vault Hunter.
Now, to draw out the Inquisitor his-self, you're gonna have to take out his gang to really get him in the goods! In a bad way!
Well, that's good to hear. I'm sure Wainwright Jakobs will do right by you for helpin' us out!
Oh, hell yeah! You blasted that one right good! One more to go! Take 'em out!
You DARE defy the will of the Calypsos?! This planet will be purged of heretics! Especially you, Vault Thief! Come and get me, if you can!
Oh, and hey—since you're on Eden-6, you might as well put this here Jakobs to good use.
Oh, those poor SOBs... Hey, Vault Hunter! Over here!

Listen... you've gotta help us put a stop to that monster. Calls himself Inquisitor Bloodflap! That sonuvabitch bastard killed my best friend, Coop! Bloodflap and his gang is on a god-dang rampage, cuttin' down innocent civilians left and right in the name of those Calypso devils! You gotta help me get some vengeance for Coop and all the others! Get yourself a vehicle and hunt those pricks down!
Well that fella sounds proper pissed. Now run 'em down and don't stop till you hear 'em squeal! Do it for Coop!

So there we were, Coop and me, just doin' our work down at the Jakobs lumbermill, then these flamin' COV nutjobs come poppin' up outta thin air, saying they're lookin' for the Jakobs Vault. Then they start callin' us all heretics and whatnot and just start murderin' everybody! It's madness! Pure madness!
Well, among other things, I'm an expert at killing COV. Leave it to me.
I never pass up a chance to kill some COV.
Fear not, fair citizen. For it is time to hunt a Bloodflap, and any COV rabble that gets in my way.
Luckily for you, I love taking out those COV bastards.
